@page "/refund-policy"

<PageTitle>Refund & Cancellation Policy</PageTitle>

<div class="legal-page">
    <h1>Refund & Cancellation Policy</h1>

    <p>
        This Refund & Cancellation Policy explains the terms under which you may cancel your booking
        and whether you are entitled to a refund. By booking our services, you agree to the following conditions:
    </p>

    <h2>1. Scooter Rentals</h2>
    <ul>
        <li>All scooter rentals are charged in full at the time of booking via Stripe.</li>
        <li>If you cancel your scooter rental <strong>at least 48 hours before</strong> the rental start time, you will receive a full refund.</li>
        <li>Cancellations made <strong>less than 48 hours</strong> before the rental start time are non-refundable.</li>
        <li>No-shows are non-refundable.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>2. Boat Rentals (without skipper)</h2>
    <ul>
        <li>A deposit of <strong>€20</strong> is charged at the time of booking via Stripe.</li>
        <li>The remaining balance must be paid on-site before the service begins.</li>
        <li>If you cancel your booking <strong>at least 72 hours before</strong> the rental start time, your deposit will be refunded in full.</li>
        <li>Cancellations made <strong>less than 72 hours</strong> before the rental start time are non-refundable.</li>
        <li>If a rental is canceled due to <strong>bad weather or safety reasons</strong> by us, your deposit will be refunded in full.</li>
        <li>No-shows are non-refundable.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>3. Private Boat Tours / Taxi Boat Services</h2>
    <ul>
        <li>A deposit of <strong>€20</strong> is charged at the time of booking via Stripe.</li>
        <li>The remaining balance must be paid on-site after the service is completed.</li>
        <li>If you cancel your booking <strong>at least 72 hours before</strong> the tour start time, your deposit will be refunded in full.</li>
        <li>Cancellations made <strong>less than 72 hours</strong> before the tour start time are non-refundable.</li>
        <li>If a tour is canceled due to <strong>bad weather or safety reasons</strong> by us, your deposit will be refunded in full.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>4. Refund Processing</h2>
    <p>
        Refunds will be issued via the original payment method (Stripe) and may take up to
        <strong>10 business days</strong> to appear in your account, depending on your bank or card provider.
    </p>

    <h2>5. Contact Us</h2>
    <p>
        If you need to request a cancellation or have questions about our refund policy,
        please contact us at:
    </p>
    <a href="mailto:taxiboatbalic@gmail.com"><strong>Email</strong>: taxiboatbaltic@gmail.com</a><br />
    <a href="tel:+385919700418"><strong>Phone</strong>: +385 91 9700 418</a>
</div>
